(clients should be repeated after the critical nature of the condition is resolved\056 The production\054 circulation\054 and disposal of Thyroid hormone are altered throughout the stages) Tj
T*
(of pregnancy\056) Tj
T*
(Hyperthyroidism \050overactive thyroid\051 \072 Hyperthyroidism \050overactive Thyroid\051 occurs when your thyroid gland produces too much of the hormone Thyroxine\056) Tj
T*
(Hyperthyroidism can accelerate your body\047s metabolism\054 causing unintentional weight loss and a rapid or irregular heartbeat\056) Tj
T*
(Hypothyroidism \050underactive thyroid\051 \072 Hypothyroidism \050underactive thyroid\051 is a condition in which your Thyroid gland doesn\047t produce enough of certain crucial) Tj
T*
(hormones\056 Hypothyroidism may not cause noticeable symptoms in the early stages\056 Over time\054 untreated Hypothyroidism can cause a number of health problems\054 such as) Tj
T*
(obesity\054 joint pain\054 infertility and heart disease\056) Tj
